title: gem-lasso
message: >-
  If you use gem-lasso in research software, analysis workflows, or academic
  writing, please cite the software record described in this file.
type: software
license: MIT
authors:
  - name: OpenAI Codex
version: 0.1.0.dev0
abstract: >-
  gem-lasso is a clean-room Python implementation of Gaussian mixture modeling
  with sparse component precision matrices, including penalized-EM and posthoc
  sparse network extraction workflows.
keywords:
  - Gaussian mixture model
  - graphical lasso
  - sparse precision matrix
  - clustering
  - research software
